I agree more or less with what my mother said,

00:10:23.500 --> 00:10:36.090
because it is true that when we come home, 
especially if it’s lunch or dinner time,

00:10:36.090 --> 00:10:43.950
we are all together in the kitchen obviously.

00:10:43.950 --> 00:10:49.060
And then each of us leaves to a different place,

00:10:49.060 --> 00:10:53.800
my mum for example goes to the living room 
or the office upstairs,

00:10:53.800 --> 00:11:01.870
my dad to his office, 
and I go to mine.

00:11:01.870 --> 00:11:13.160
