as you said, the good thing is that

00:15:58.200 --> 00:16:04.160
it’s not only a meeting point 
and also where we eat, it’s also

00:16:04.160 --> 00:16:12.700
sort of a second leisure room, 
because if you can’t watch TV

00:16:12.700 --> 00:16:17.300
in the living room you can just watch it here.

00:16:17.300 --> 00:16:19.940
For example, I often watch football here

00:16:19.940 --> 00:16:28.750
in the kitchen because I can’t in the living room, 
because it’s taken, and...that’s it,

00:16:28.750 --> 00:16:35.540
or sometimes I watch a show here or...

00:16:35.540 --> 00:16:42.228
Or you watch the news here, 
which is the usual instead of in the living room.

00:16:43.908 --> 00:16:44.786
So...

00:16:47.670 --> 00:16:48.170
Yes.

